//
//  Config.xcconfig.example
//
//  Copy this file to Config.xcconfig (gitignored, never committed) and fill
//  in your own personal Apple Developer team ID so Xcode can sign locally
//  without touching anything the rest of the team relies on.
//
//  Find your team ID in Xcode > Settings > Accounts > select your Apple ID > Team.
//
//  The bundle identifier (com.urbananTaggo.app) is NOT per-developer -- it's
//  fixed and tracked in the project itself, because the iCloud container and
//  App Clip parent-identifier entitlements must be one stable, literal string
//  to register with Apple at all (custom xcconfig variables don't reliably
//  resolve in that registration path). Only your own signing team is local.
//
DEVELOPMENT_TEAM = YOUR_TEAM_ID_HERE
